query: WITH entities AS (SELECT policy_id, id FROM approval_processes WHERE (COALESCE((policy_id, id) < ($3, $2), $2 IS NULL)) ORDER BY policy_id DESC, id DESC LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: ApprovalProcessId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN approval_process_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.policy_id desc, i.id desc, i.id, e.sequence
